The Singing Killer
programme.desc: Chiang Yi is blackmailed into a jewellery heist by his former boss, who threatens to expose his shady past. Complications arise when he discovers his first love works at the store.

programme.title: The Twin Bracelets
programme.desc: When two childhood friends in a remote community vow to live as sisters forever, the stage is set for a drama of tragic proportions when, years later, one leaves to get married.

programme.title: The Comedy Of Mismatches
programme.desc: Two pairs of lovers got mismatched accidentally. The man disguises as a woman for his sister's wedding ceremony, while his lover disguises as a man to marry another woman.

programme.title: The Fighting Fool
programme.desc: It's Meng Yuan-wen versus Kuan Feng in this wild and wacky wushu saga of a priceless pole with a spectacular secret.

programme.title: Asia-Pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister.

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: Three girls travel to Japan to collect an unexpected inheritance, only to be met by three guys there to do the same. So begins a vicious battle to receive what was promised them.

programme.title: Tales Of A Eunuch
programme.desc: The story follows a 'loveable' rascal as he gambles and gets into various bits of trouble with outlaws and rebels. The whole movie revolves around a quest for all the copies of a special Buddhist text.

programme.title: Gossip Street
programme.desc: Shaw Bros and TVB stars unite for Wang Feng's ensemble epic. Trouble is brewing when a gangster plans to change the Gossip Street residents' favourite hangout into a gambling den.

programme.title: Twin Blades Of Doom
programme.desc: A retired martial artist is forced back into action after his family is murdered by the evil Ghost Gang. Without friends, he is forced to ally himself with a quintet of killers.

programme.title: The Grand Substitution
programme.desc: This Huangmei Opera epic stars Li Li-hua and Ivy Ling Po in the story of a loyal Imperial Court servant who gives up his own newborn son to save the prince from an evil official.

programme.title: Heaven Sword & Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: In the Yuan Dynasty, martial artists everywhere battle for the Heaven Sword and the Dragon Sabre. When these two powerful weapons combine, can a secret be revealed to help one become the king of the martial arts world.

programme.title: Love With The Perfect Stranger
programme.desc: After breaking up with his girlfriend, salesman Bao meets a rich girl, Jin Jin, who just broke up with her boyfriend. Two equally heartbroken strangers fall in love instantly and get married on impulse.

programme.title: The Lady Professional
programme.desc: Lily Ho stars as a seductive hit woman in this contemporary Shaw Bros action thriller. Filmed in HK and Japan the story follows Ho's assassin as she discovers she is now a target.

programme.title: A Friend From Inner Space
programme.desc: Perennial martial-arts villain Shek Kin takes on a rare comedic role as a playful ghost who befriends a young boy and helps him reunite his feuding parents.

programme.title: West Chamber
programme.desc: The story is based on a famous Chinese opera. A young impoverished scholar, Zhang, is enchanted by Hong, the daughter of an influential family whom he meets in a temple.

programme.title: Twelve Deadly Coins
programme.desc: When Qiao Miao is about to kill the bandit whom he just met, he is attracted by her beauty and they quickly fall in love. The two later discover the blood feud between the owner of the unique weapon.

programme.title: The Shadow Whip
programme.desc: Three hundred thousand silver is robbed by a thief using a whip as the weapon. As it is a signature weapon used by a martial arts master named 'Shadow Whip', he is suspected and hunted.

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read Ching Dynasty novel, this touching love story has proven a challenge to many filmmakers. A classic combination of both 18th century literature and 1960s moviemaking.

programme.title: Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A Wu Dang disciple Fu, kills the chief of Wu Dang Clan and frames it on the chief's illegitimate child, Yun. Fu then proclaims himself the new chief and orders the killing of Yun, who vows to avenge his father's death.

programme.title: Fangs Of The Cobra
programme.desc: This unique thriller betrays its ominous title by telling the story of a heroic and virtuous serpent who unearths traps, battles a baby-eating rodent and even wards off rival gangs.

programme.title: Demon Of The Lute
programme.desc: Lute demon Chin Mo has reappeared in the world to wreak havoc. Hsiao Feng-ling is ordered to find a special bow and arrows that can counter the demon.

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: As punishment for bad behaviour, the Jade Emperor's 7th daughter is banished from heaven and sent to live with the humans. There she falls in love with young villager, Dong Young.

programme.title: Mission Impossible
programme.desc: A sword master's daughter is pursued and poisoned by an evil master when bringing back the stolen Golden Sword to the palace.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: An award winning movie for best script and best editing. Another tale of a Sino-Japanese war that artistically and emotional triumphed, it clearly portrays the life of wartime.

programme.title: The 14 Amazons
programme.desc: The Yang family had served their country in Song Dynasty for generations. When General Yang is ambushed and killed during the war in Jin Shan, the grand matriarch led the family to take revenge and defend the country.

programme.title: Inside The Forbidden City
programme.desc: Justice Bao discovers that Consort Li's new born son was swapped at birth and that she was expelled from the palace by Empress Liu twenty years ago. He sets Eunuch Guo up to confess his conspiracy with the Empress.

programme.title: The Kung-Fu Instructor
programme.desc: Wong Yang is a famous martial artist who is forced to teach kung fu to the Mong Clan, an evil clan which is trying to destroy its nemesis, the Chow Clan.

programme.title: The Tiger And The Widow
programme.desc: In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: Lovers Blades
programme.desc: Forbidden love and magical weapons are at the centre of this enjoyable martial arts comedy. A reunited couple must recover the titular swords and avenge a murder from their past!

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide.

programme.title: All Men Are Brothers
programme.desc: The patriotic story of seven warriors in the band of 108 outlaws at Mount Liang. The magnificent seven battle against the despotic government officials to save their country.

programme.title: The Bride From Hell
programme.desc: The 70s idol Hsing Hui and Yon Fan star in this horror movie. Young business man marries pretty, young bride, never knowing that she carries the spirit and everything starts there.

programme.title: The Lady Hermit
programme.desc: The Lady Hermit hides away for years to plot revenge after being defeated by the evil Black Knight. Young swordswoman Tsui Ping is determined to take down Black Knight herself and begs to teach her martial arts skills.

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: Yu Nan (Yi Lei) is a compulsive gambler. He makes his wife as a down payment for his debt, feeling regretted and decides to kill himself but stops when a beautiful ghost appears.

programme.title: One Way Only
programme.desc: Acclaimed actor Danny Lee plays a motorbike workshop owner who injured during an illegal motorcycle race and continues to race regardless of the physical consequences and the law.

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: Director Chan Friend created this delightful variation on the British 'Carry On!' film series. It can certainly make you laugh with all the comical acts happened in the Hospital!

programme.title: The Twelve Gold Medallions
programme.desc: The evil minister uses the twelve golden medallions, the highest imperial decree, to summon war hero Yueh Fei back from the frontline and execute him. A group of wandering warriors try to stop the medallion couriers.

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical production serves as a showcase for personable singer/actor George Lam, who tries to find love and success in the world of TV commercials along with his buddies Hamburger and Snoopy.

programme.title: Full Moon Scimitar
programme.desc: Swordsman Peng fought against many swordsmen and won, so he couldn't accept his first defeat and wanted to suicide. The Sect leader gives him the 'Full Moon Scimitar' on the condition that he will never leave the sect.

programme.title: Black Magic
programme.desc: Martial arts stalwart Ti Lung is transformed as a helpless man caught in the spell of an evil witch doctor, who will do whatever it takes to take his client's bride for himself.

programme.title: Legend Of The Bat
programme.desc: Charismatic swordsman Chu Liu Hsiang, whose battlefield exploits rival his bedroom antics, travels to the Island of Bats, where he encounters monks, women and plenty of action!

programme.title: Urban Cops S1, Ep 9
programme.desc: Upon completion of their basic training, actors transform into police detectives and join Yongsan Criminal Intelligence Unit to track down criminals.

programme.title: Run Puppy Run, Ep 8
programme.desc: In this variety show, dog-loving celebrities team up with their dogs for the biggest dog agility competition in Korea.

programme.title: Yacht...: The Beginning, Ep 7
programme.desc: In the second season, a group of celebrities takes on the challenge of sailing a yacht, they have to overcome rigorous training before finally mastering it and enjoying the exciting voyage.

programme.title: Munitions Hijacking Case
